            <p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.3994399070739745;margin-left: 14.227228164672852pt;margin-right: 4.171630859375pt;text-indent: 0.01999950408935547pt;margin-top:24.285797119140625pt"><span style="font-size:10pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap">We receive some information from the third parties when you contact us. For example, when you submit your email address to us to show interest in becoming a Sawtru Boost Website customer, we receive information from a third party that provides automated fraud detection services to Sawtru Boost Website. We also occasionally collect information that is made publicly available on social media websites. You can control how much of your information social media websites make public by visiting these websites and changing your privacy settings.&nbsp;</span></p>
